data.description: This move in ready, freshly painted 3 beds, 1 bath Ranch is all done for you! With Beautiful , New York Sash Windows (lifetime transferable warranty - 2021) New central air (2019), Updated Electrical for outside security lights and all new light fixtures throughout. Exterior paint and landscaping to finish out the beautiful look on the outside. Basement has TONS of storage, washer/ dryer hookups and a partially finished room. One stall attached garage, leads to basement or the upstairs. Amazing corner lot with privacy fence on one side and a stone wall on the other. Country Living - Lee taxes and Rome Schools. Who's ready to check this one out.
